ssets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\nTwitter文宣組<br />\n戰線台 @twittermansyunzou <br />\n<br />\nReddit戰線 @reddithk_channel<br />\n文宣 @hkstandstrong_promo_int @guardiansofhongkong<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppespe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=a1a04879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n做任務，推任務，整圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K7BL6RX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK7BL6RX.jpg&h=9eb54208&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fpGsALi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfpGsALi.jpg&h=3e144153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJyR2qj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJyR2qj.jpg&h=8f296929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s2w8kb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs2w8kb2.png&h=8709b2bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ff643b60db77f2a52c9b02b6d5d219c24fbfc0b","tid":1977431,"uid":56744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:41:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68bdbf0f8dace688709d84883588a0c36ca0fe8f","tid":1977431,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:11:43.000Z","msg":"UP"},{"pid":"0fb84767a046df71c77aa2f3916a4d2b9d1bf096","tid":1977431,"uid":235579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"353a152333e24089313cd253cb4e9c67361cf00a","tid":1977431,"uid":63382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:28:29.000Z","msg":"見黃店有嘈交就不斷扮下兩邊互屌<br />\n再係連登開個標題撚topic帶風向<br />\n再繼續係連登互屌撥火<br />\n<br />\n每一次有任何傷亡新聞就仆出黎講「手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」「好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n再笑鳩你地咩都做唔到<br />\n係咪覺得好反感？<br />\n因為佢地想塑造示威者係一個神憎鬼厭嘅人<br />\n<br />\n大量反送中紅底書已經傾巢而出<br />\n歷史從來都係勝利一方寫<br />\n如果大家呢個時間仲係互相批鬥打泥漿摔角<br />\n仲對唔對得住過往為大家付出過嘅義士？<br />\n<br />\n都差唔多經歷咗成年<br />\n大家以上嘅手法可能大家好清楚<br />\n我只希望大家勿忘初衷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T16:58:23.000Z","msg":"幫手推， 一定要回覆理性討論，任何亂吠嘅人都要當五毛"},{"pid":"d1426bcd6a057b957b15c6a56d0bbf37fd52884c","tid":1977431,"uid":235579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"864aca8586895f310be86773096b656a8f54fc3e","tid":1977431,"uid":84668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yvs3PGt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvs3PGt.jpg&h=0f532aa9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n由五四運動開始 再到8964  共產黨講到依家既 &quot;煽動學生論&quot;<br />\n<br />\n在呢個post入面(26樓)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1976874/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1976874/page/2</a><br />\n竟然有咁多人俾正評<br />\n就知入面好多五毛, 同埋連登仔係好易俾人帶風向<br />\n<br />\n大家真係要好好睇路<br />\n連登已經俾五毛渗透晒<br />\n有一班p牌仔扮低等五毛, 好易俾你發現<br />\n等你地以為佢地就係連登全部既五毛<br />\n另外再有一班高等五毛, 個acc可能係偷被殺或被捕既手足<br />\n冇p牌, 講野有文有路, 會講8成好岩聽既野, 但會加入少量關鍵既洗腦說話或破壞運動既說話 (如上圖條友講&quot;煽動學生論&quot;, &quot;運動已完&quot;, &quot;學生返去溫書唔好理政治&quot;等等)<br />\n<br />\n希望有能力既巴打可以綜合言論, 開個整合post出黎警世"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:00:29.000Z","msg":"一定要小心五毛。<br />\n<br />\n連登仔唔可以太易被人帶風向"},{"pid":"9f6c030b090d9757ea1c524331c85c98266ecebc","tid":1977431,"uid":176996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:20:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"08a4a51f773e8e1d10ddd538757af302f089bff2","tid":1977431,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"（社評）三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671672</a>"},{"pid":"d5ece966e46fa51c2595241ddd6a302cff020598","t